@startuml
title analysis-stt - 음성 transcript Celery Worker 내부 구조

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
}
skinparam component<<external>> {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #607D8B
}
skinparam component<<model>> {
  BackgroundColor #C8E6C9
  BorderColor #43A047
}

queue "Redis\n(analysis-stt queue)" as Redis <<external>>
component "Backend\n(콜백 task)" as BE <<external>>
database "S3 (scaled-audio-files)" as S3 <<external>>

package "analysis-stt/" {
  component "celery_app.py\nconfig.py" as Cfg

  package "tasks/" {
    component "transcribe_audio_task\n(BaseTask)" as TaskMain
  }

  package "services/" {
    component "TranscribeService\n(S3 다운로드 → STT → 결과 반환)" as Svc
    component "WhisperEngine\n(Singleton)\nfaster-whisper model" as Whisper <<model>>
    component "S3 Loader\n(boto3.download_fileobj)" as S3L
  }
}

Redis --> TaskMain : pull task (audio_key, turn_id)
TaskMain --> Svc : transcribe(audio_key)
Svc --> S3L : download
S3L --> S3 : GET .wav (16kHz mono)
S3L --> Svc : in-memory bytes
Svc --> Whisper : transcribe(audio, language=ko)
Whisper --> Svc : segments + text
Svc --> TaskMain : transcript text

TaskMain --> Redis : callback (Backend save_transcript)
Redis --> BE

note bottom of Whisper
  faster-whisper:
  - 모델 1회 로드 후 메모리 상주
  - GPU 없을 시 CPU INT8 quantize
  - 한국어 디코딩 최적화
end note

footer analysis-stt/ — faster-whisper Singleton · CPU INT8 · 16kHz mono 입력
@enduml
